Pre-Game Insights: Both Namibia and Scotland topped their regional qualifiers with six wins from six.
Namibia needs to secure two wins from two to go top of Group B.
Scotland needs a win to maintain their 100% record in T20Is against Oman.
George Munsey and Ruben Trumpelmann are key performers for Namibia and Scotland respectively.
Munsey previously scored a century against Scotland in 2021 but was dismissed early in that match.
Trumpelmann has taken two wickets in his first two overs against Oman.
The match is scheduled for 8 pm local time in Bridgetown, Barbados.
